						<button class="sheet-close static" id="helpClose" aria-label="Close">✕</button>
					</div>
					<button class="sheet-btn" id="reopenSetup" style="width:100%;margin-bottom:.6rem">👋 Re-open the setup guide</button>
					<ul class="help-list">
						<li><b>🎸 Schedule</b> — every Centeroo set with live <i>NOW</i> badges. Tap a set for the artist's photo, bio, socials, news and Spotify. Tap ☆ to save it to My Roo. Search looks at today first, then shows matches from other days below. Hit <b>Now</b> to jump to the current moment.</li>
						<li><b>🗺️ Map</b> — satellite map of the Farm. 📍 live location + distance to every stage, water and medical (auto-reconnects when signal drops). ⛺ custom pins for camps and meetup spots. 🧭 a compass that points straight back to your camp at 2 AM. 📜 the official festival maps. Chips toggle 🌧️ live rain radar and ➤ your route — yellow arrows through today's ★ sets in order.</li>
						<li><b>⭐ My Roo</b> — your plan, day by day: overlap warnings, 🚶 leave-by walking times between stages, 📅 export to your calendar for offline reminders. <b>Share</b> sends a link carrying your whole plan, or hit <b>⊞ QR</b> for a fullscreen code anyone can scan — no app needed. Friends' plans you open get saved with 🤝 overlap markers.</li>
						<li><b>🐾 Tracks</b> — while 📍 is on, your wandering is drawn as a trail on the map. Toggle the 🐾 chip to see where you've roamed.</li>
						<li><b>🧭 Guide</b> — live forecast + storm alerts, gate rules, what you can bring, water/medical info, and official links.</li>
						<li><b>Works offline-ish</b> — once loaded, the app and official maps keep working with no signal; only live tiles, radar and weather need a connection. Your plan and pins are saved on your phone.</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="help-install">
						<button class="sheet-btn sheet-primary" id="installBtn" hidden>📲 Install as an app</button>
