						</p>
					</div>
					<p class="help-foot">Unofficial &amp; fan-made. Set times can change — the official Festiverse app has the final word.</p>
					<p class="help-foot">Privacy: this app collects anonymous usage analytics — taps, selections, approximate location/movement and device info — to understand how it's used and improve it. No accounts, no names sold; data is tied to a random device ID, not your identity.</p>
